alazł!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/33303/size6/8e7de6ecb2c328f22ec886f391920be9.jpg","text":"Teraz muszę zejść z drzewa.\nPrzytulam się do babci.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":6,"words":60}}